transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Rajesh ji baat kar raha hu IndiaMART se.
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Haan ji.
Customer: Boliye.
Executive: Sir, sir ji aap se baat hui thi, maine customer ko bhi ek call aapka theek tha kiya tha 10:15 baje.
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Bataiye sir, leads to abhi bhi available hai sir. Dekhiye calcite powder ki ek hamare paas Gujarat se mil rahi hai sir 25 ton ki. To baat karke dekhiye ek baar aap.
Customer: Nahi, nahi mere paas mein itna time nahi hai.
Executive: To aapne theek tha kiya hai sir, thoda sa aap
